window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>It’s hard for S. Beaufont to imagine that dragons were nearly extinct when they’re now hatching so rapidly. However, for every good dragon, there’s an evil one. That’s the way the angels set it up.</p> <p>But can things be changed? Can an evil dragon turn good? And if so, is it possible a good one can switch, too?</p> <p>As new evils lurk in the world, Sophia works to manage the new population at the Gullington. Never before were there so many possibilities for maintaining justice. But never before were there so many trying to break the law. Can the Dragon Elite uphold justice, or will they be overrun?</p>"; 
